{#-
Institution dossier page skeleton (Constitution III.13 / Amendment W).

Deliberately prose-free: this is a scaffold page, not narrative copy. Every
value interpolated here is a plain string already resolved by
babylon.projection.vault.render_institution (never a raw Optional
InstitutionView field — Jinja's StrictUndefined only fires on genuinely
*absent* names, and a present-but-None field renders the literal text "None"
rather than raising, so render_institution.py precomputes
statblock_rows/absent_fields and the template only ever touches those and
the three always-present identity fields).

Fenced directives only ({statblock}/{absence}), matching
babylon.tui.directives.BabylonFence dispatch (ADR099: paired containers
break the 8.2.8 markdown walker).
-#}
